We're using Stripe checkout in order to be able to

Stripe is a payment processing tool that connects to the bank and does the payment process.
In real-world businesses, using a third-party checkout page is recommended beside Stripe.
It allows businesses to process credit and debit card.


Stripe is a full-stack payment processor, meaning it serves as both a payment processor and a payment gateway.
To process online transactions you need both.

In order to user Stripe REST API, you'll need two pair of public/private keys, one test and one live.

